add_day_item

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_day_item -  This method sets up an item which will only be displayed during the day.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int add_day_item(mixed shorts,
mixed desc,
mixed no_plural)
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic_room.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets up an item which will only be displayed during the
day.  All of the standard add_item things are available with this
method.
.EP

